Package: rodin-rc
Architecture: amd64
Depends: default-jre | java-runtime,
         libgtk-3-0t64 | libgtk-3-0,
         hicolor-icon-theme,
         ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0
Provides: rodin
Conflicts: rodin
Replaces: rodin
Description: Eclipse-based IDE for Event-B (release candidate)
 The Rodin platform is an Eclipse-based integrated development environment for
 Event-B. It supports refinement, mathematical proof, type-checking and the
 generation and discharge of proof obligations, and is extensible through a wide
 range of plug-ins.
 .
 This package provides a pre-release (release candidate) build of Rodin and is a
 drop-in replacement for the stable "rodin" package, with which it conflicts. A
 Java runtime is required; webkit2gtk is recommended for the browser-backed
 views.
